{"TopicId":142274,"ForumId":20,"TopicTitle":"\u0026quot;only IVA mode\u0026quot; possible?","CreatedByName":"Speadge","CreatedById":145302,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-22T18:37:43Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Speadge","CreatedById":145302,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-22T18:37:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHey,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nim desperately looking for a config / mod that lets me disable the 3rd person camera and force me to do everything in IVA - is there anything to do so?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nwould also be a great addition to\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/142257-113-kerbal-kommander-a-new-way-to-play-ksp/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-22T18:38:43Z\u0022 title=\u002206/22/2016 06:38  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 22, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Speadge\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nansuchao","CreatedById":135151,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T08:57:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs far as I know, what you\u0027re asking isn\u0027t still implemented. Btw, with the help of some mods, you can reach your goal. For example, with the right command pod and the IVA from Alexustas, you can do everything from IVA, launch, rendez-vous, docking and generally controlling your ship completely.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Speadge","CreatedById":145302,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T09:13:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222643226\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142274\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466672259\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022135151\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nansuchao\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n13 minutes ago, Nansuchao said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs far as I know, what you\u0027re asking isn\u0027t still implemented. Btw, with the help of some mods, you can reach your goal. For example, with the right command pod and the IVA from Alexustas, you can do everything from IVA, launch, rendez-vous, docking and generally controlling your ship completely.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nactually it lacks more in the \u0022transition\u0022 of the scenes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nfor example there is a mod that directly enters IVA on shipload - thats great, but u still can change back to 3rd person.\u003Cbr\u003E\nalso it may be hard to get on EVA while in IVA view...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo im basically looking for something that addresses those two gaps - may have missed one \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Malah","CreatedById":96644,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T15:34:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222643242\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142274\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466673186\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145302\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Speadge\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, Speadge said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nthanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nactually it lacks more in the \u0022transition\u0022 of the scenes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nfor example there is a mod that directly enters IVA on shipload - thats great, but u still can change back to 3rd person.\u003Cbr\u003E\nalso it may be hard to get on EVA while in IVA view...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSo im basically looking for something that addresses those two gaps - may have missed one \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuickIVA locked the possibility to go to the 3rd person, if not it is a bug \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/85834-1\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Speadge","CreatedById":145302,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T15:36:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222643672\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142274\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466696097\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002296644\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Malah\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Malah said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nQuickIVA locked the possibility to go to the 3rd person, if not it is a bug \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/85834-1\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncool, did u actually LOCK it? just thought its entering IVA on vessel load, but you can change back any time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do you go EVA then?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Malah","CreatedById":96644,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T15:39:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222643675\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142274\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466696192\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145302\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Speadge\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Speadge said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncool, did u actually LOCK it? just thought its entering IVA on vessel load, but you can change back any time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow do you go EVA then?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAt this time it lock the view, there\u0027s shortcut to EVA and to recover your vessel ...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAll functions you have :\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022F4Y00c