3E\u003C/abbr\u003E?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNo problem, you can do what you want \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Evanitis","CreatedById":145424,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T15:50:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wouldn\u0027t forget about Raster Prop Monitor either.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/105821-113-rasterpropmonitor-still-putting-the-a-in-iva-v0270-22-june-2016/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m using it for too long, so forgot how stock IVA looks like. Though it lets you to do virtually anything from IVA, without ever switching to map or outside view. In case you really don\u0027t want to.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-06-23T15:50:54Z\u0022 title=\u002206/23/2016 03:50  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EJune 23, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Evanitis\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Speadge","CreatedById":145302,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T15:51:34Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222643699\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142274\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466697021\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145424\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Evanitis\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, Evanitis said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI wouldn\u0027t forget about Raster Prop Monitor either.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/105821-113-rasterpropmonitor-still-putting-the-a-in-iva-v0270-22-june-2016/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m using it for too long, so forgot how stock IVA looks like. Though it lets you to do virtually anything from IVA, without ever switching to map or outside view. If you really want to.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nalready planned this in, thanks\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsee this\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/142257-113-kerbal-kommander-a-new-way-to-play-ksp/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;embedComment=2643698\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Evanitis","CreatedById":145424,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T15:53:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s on my list of cool stuff to try since it\u0027s release. I\u0027m just waiting for some \u0027can\u0027t live without\u0027 mods to update. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022^_^\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_happy.png\u0022 title=\u0022^_^\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Speadge","CreatedById":145302,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T15:54:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/96644-malah/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002296644\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/96644-malah/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Malah\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0thanks for your time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs i understood i need to use the hotkey to go eva then.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsorry for asking, but could u add a button for it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nis it possible to change kerbals in IVA / see which one is the selected one?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Malah","CreatedById":96644,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-06-23T16:09:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222643707\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022142274\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221466697266\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022145302\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Speadge\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, Speadge said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/96644-malah/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002296644\u0022 href=\u0022%7B___base_url___%7D/index.php?/profile/96644-malah/\u0022 rel=\u0022external\u0022\u003E@Malah\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0thanks for your time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAs i understood i need to use the hotkey to go eva then.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nsorry for asking, but could u add a button for it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nis it possible to change kerbals in IVA / see which one is the selected one?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSorry, I wont add a button for this, perhaps RPM has something like this?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWith the stock shortcut you can change kerbals (don\u0027t remember which). And each time you change kerbal a msg screen appear to say which kerbal you have and his job \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022;)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}